### Crear un nuevo Objetivo
POST {{baseUrl}}/objectives
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "target_amount": 2000,
  "objective_name": "Objetivo de prueba 2",
  "current_amount": 0,
